*[[Bob Hope]] (1977)
*[[Kareem Abdul-Jabbar]] (1989)
*[[Whoopi Goldberg]] (1990)
*[[Nelson Mandela]] (1996)
*[[Jackie Joyner-Kersee]] (1999)
